Description_lang: Nymue marks targeted players coalescing verdant needles poised to strike. Moments later these blitz forward knocking away and inflicting $s1 Nature damage to other players along the travel path. Upon reaching their target they explode inflicting $427137s2 Nature damage and an additional $427138s1 Nature damage every $427138t1 sec for $427138d to all players, reducing to $427138s1 Nature damage every $427138t1 sec for $427138d on only the marked target if they passed through the $@spellname418423.
